      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-shares-plunge-16-frankfurt-after-ai-spending-revenue-forecast-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四法兰克福早盘，Meta Platforms 股价暴跌 16%，原因是费用高于预期、收入低于预期，令投资者感到失望。]]></description>
